    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/52" key="#Popes">Paschalis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2500" key="#Abbots">Hoddoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">mon.</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53" key="#Monasteries">S. Sisti</orgName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/43">Placentie</placeName>. Sapientium ac
                        religiosorum virorum consilio provisum est agente precipue illustris memorie
                            <persName ref="#people/125" key="#Countess">Matildi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs> ut in eodem monasterio pro feminis viri
                        ponerentur quatinus et religio illic eiusdem idest monastici ordini
                        servaretur et monasterii possessiones quÄ™ iamdiu distracte fuerant per eorum
                        ecstituerentur industriam. Hanc igitur mutationem in loci illius ordinatione
                        dispositam nos per presentis privilegii paginam confirmamus. Ipsum vero
                        locum et universa ad eum pertinentia sub apostolice sedis tutela et
                        protectione servanda censemus. Statuimus etiam ut universa predia vel
                        possessiones quas <persName ref="#people/55" key="#Queen"
                            >Angelberga</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatrix</rs> eiusdem mon. fondatrix illuc contulisse
                        cognoscitur et quecumque legitime pertinent ad ipsum mon. firma et illibata
                        permaneant. Decernimnus ergo ut nulli omnino hominum liceat idem monasterium
                        temere perturbare; obeunte te fratres communi consensu novum abbatem
                        providerint eligendum. Quicquid preterea libertatis seu dignitatis a
                        predecessoribus nostris concessum est nos quooque concedimus. - (Legimus in
                        prophetis.) Scriptum p. m. <persName key="#Notary #Scriniarius"><name
                                ref="Gervasius">Gervasii</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scriniarius">scrin.</rs> regionarii ac <rs key="#Notary">not.</rs>
                        s. pal. (Ego Paschalis etc.). . . , Dat. Laterani p. m. <persName
                            key="#Deacons #Cardinals"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName> S. R. E. <rs key="#Deacons">diac.</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">card.</rs> ac bibl., III kal. nov., ind. IX, inc. dom.
                        an. MCXV, pontif. Autem d. Paschalis II <rs key="#Popes">pp.</rs> an.
                        XVII</ab>
